On Escalation Ticket # 00424427 the new comment has been added: Hi Team,

This is the correct ticket where the comment was made.
We could not access the end users computer to generate log files.
What we saw in the EPP UI was that almost all device types(WIfi, Local Printers, Network Printers, Keyboards, etc) had duplicates.

Please provide me with a full list of device_type_id(for all device types) so I can run the below command and delete the duplicate devices:
delete from clientdevice where device_type_id = 45 order by id desc limit 10000;

Thank you!
Flaviu
